<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>宁德时代称已获发改委批准20亿美元外债额度</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200909/0a9eae66655d497f85fe3d7a4d932af1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
